{"id":334495,"type":2,"name":"180秒で君の耳を幸せにできるか？","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dd/75/334495_DbKjh.jpg","summary":"180秒で登場人物を通じ、ASMRの魅力を伝える。\r\n\r\nASMRとは「Autonomous Sensory Meridian Response（自律感覚絶頂反応）」の略語で、聴覚や視覚への刺激によって脳がゾワゾワしたりリラックスするような反応・感覚のこと。「180秒で君の耳を幸せにできるか？」はタイトルの通り180秒という時間の中で、色々なASMRを体験することができるショートアニメ。","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>*</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2021年10月</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/37248\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">葛西良信</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/3810\">野口孝行</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/41637\">INDIVISION</a>、<a href=\"/person/31986\">EKACHI EPILKA</a></li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://180-kimimimi.jp/</li><li><span>Copyright: </span>© 君耳製作委員会</li>","collection":{"wish":4,"collect":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"INDIVISION","count":2},{"name":"2021年","count":2},{"name":"EkachiEpilka","count":2},{"name":"日本动画","count":1},{"name":"葛西良信","count":1},{"name":"泡面番","count":1},{"name":"2021","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":37248,"image":"","name":"葛西良信","desc":"导演"},{"id":3810,"image":"","name":"野口孝行","desc":"人物设定"},{"id":41637,"image":"","name":"INDIVISION","desc":"动画制作"},{"id":31986,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/83/71/31986_prsn_K5fDa.jpg","name":"EKACHI EPILKA","desc":"动画制作"}]}